title: Mike Calta, Galvin, Jenn Sterger, & ME
description: From 102.5 The Bone in Tampa, The Mike Calta Show - Cowhead (aka Mike Calta), Galvin, Jenn Sterger, & I hang out in Tampa before the Call In Sick to Work Show and play a BEST OF from my times on the Cowhead Show/Mike Calta Show, haze Jenn Sterger, and are all drunk.  Thank you @AngryGalvin for editting this episode!!!
